  "detailed_description": "<br><br><strong>Journey to Monolith</strong> is a strategic, turn-based roguelite game.  Choose a general to lead your team, recruit fighters from six unique regions, and customize your fighters' stats and abilities with powerful spells.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730290/extras/a7b458cc16f88069852e6cd550fa95e2.avif?t=1722513597\" width=500 height=255 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730290/extras/b631d30fee71f339380223a1a6300c84.poster.avif?t=1722513597\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730290/extras/b631d30fee71f339380223a1a6300c84.webm?t=1722513597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730290/extras/b631d30fee71f339380223a1a6300c84.mp4?t=1722513597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Create a different team every time with over 50 different units from six distinctive factions: Lyonar Kingdoms, Songhai Empire, Vetruvian Imperium, Abyssian Host, Magmar Aspects, and Vanar Kindred.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730290/extras/554f6846e31c7bfcae05f7f29f2e4bad.poster.avif?t=1722513597\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730290/extras/554f6846e31c7bfcae05f7f29f2e4bad.webm?t=1722513597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730290/extras/554f6846e31c7bfcae05f7f29f2e4bad.mp4?t=1722513597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Discover formidable and synergistic spells to enhance your units, find emergent combos, and overwhelm the enemy.<br></li><li>Travel through 6 different regions and attempt to reach the Monolith where your final foe awaits.</li></ul><br><br>Journey to Monolith has no affiliation with Counterplay Games. I want to thank them for releasing so much of the original Duelyst source code under a Creative Commons license in 2022",
